THIRD-PARTY MODELS & COMPONENTS

LingoLens downloads and uses third-party models at runtime; each retains its own
license:
  - PP-OCRv5 / RapidOCR ............ Apache-2.0
  - Qwen3 (translation) ............ Apache-2.0
  - Opus-MT / Helsinki-NLP (zh-en)  CC-BY-4.0 (attribution required; translation
                                    model by the Language Technology Research
                                    Group at the University of Helsinki — OPUS-MT,
                                    Tiedemann & Thottingal)

Models under non-commercial terms (e.g. NLLB, CC-BY-NC) and custom terms (e.g.
Gemma) are intentionally NOT used.
